{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"cebf2bd5cc8bb777ea20e6","title":"2026-05-19 WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367060,"created":1780371330026,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-19_WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"295da44d0af237a9ce68cd615f7a0de5","links":[{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","id":"bk7252n-ai-printer","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":3,"offset":1320},"end":{"line":37,"column":57,"offset":1374},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-19_WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录"},{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","id":"62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":45,"offset":3856},"end":{"line":30,"column":99,"offset":3910},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.2026-05-19_WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录"}],"anchors":{"2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"2026-05-19 WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录","value":"2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"需求背景":{"type":"header","text":"需求背景","value":"需求背景","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"优化目标":{"type":"header","text":"优化目标","value":"优化目标","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"技术方案演进":{"type":"header","text":"技术方案演进","value":"技术方案演进","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"第1版1bpp1bpp原有方案效果差":{"type":"header","text":"第1版：1bpp→1bpp（原有方案，效果差）","value":"第1版1bpp1bpp原有方案效果差","line":22,"column":0,"depth":3},"第2版1bpp4bpp过渡方案内存溢出":{"type":"header","text":"第2版：1bpp→4bpp（过渡方案，内存溢出）","value":"第2版1bpp4bpp过渡方案内存溢出","line":35,"column":0,"depth":3},"第3版1bpp2bpp最终方案质量与内存平衡":{"type":"header","text":"第3版：1bpp→2bpp（最终方案，质量与内存平衡）","value":"第3版1bpp2bpp最终方案质量与内存平衡","line":55,"column":0,"depth":3},"涉及文件":{"type":"header","text":"涉及文件","value":"涉及文件","line":71,"column":0,"depth":2},"核心算法细节":{"type":"header","text":"核心算法细节","value":"核心算法细节","line":79,"column":0,"depth":2},"1-中心加权区域采样":{"type":"header","text":"1. 中心加权区域采样","value":"1-中心加权区域采样","line":81,"column":0,"depth":3},"2-稀疏墨点增强":{"type":"header","text":"2. 稀疏墨点增强","value":"2-稀疏墨点增强","line":94,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-2bpp-量化":{"type":"header","text":"3. 2bpp 量化","value":"3-2bpp-量化","line":103,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-自动反色检测":{"type":"header","text":"4. 自动反色检测","value":"4-自动反色检测","line":118,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-蛇形扫描serpentine":{"type":"header","text":"5. 蛇形扫描（Serpentine）","value":"5-蛇形扫描serpentine","line":123,"column":0,"depth":3},"调色板反色问题修复":{"type":"header","text":"调色板反色问题修复","value":"调色板反色问题修复","line":127,"column":0,"depth":2},"参数配置":{"type":"header","text":"参数配置","value":"参数配置","line":134,"column":0,"depth":2},"内存对比":{"type":"header","text":"内存对比","value":"内存对比","line":146,"column":0,"depth":2},"日志诊断":{"type":"header","text":"日志诊断","value":"日志诊断","line":154,"column":0,"depth":2},"待优化方向":{"type":"header","text":"待优化方向","value":"待优化方向","line":164,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"wn668uyx88v4u3xlc5q5uka","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录\">2026-05-19 WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录-1\">2026-05-19 WS热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-19-ws热敏图预览压缩质量优化开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"需求背景\">需求背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#需求背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>云端下发图片数据（MQTT binary, 1bpp 热敏位图, 384宽）经过压缩后在 245×245 预览框中显示，原有方案直接将 1bpp 源图缩放→抖动→1bpp 输出，压缩后的图片在屏幕上锯齿严重、细节丢失、抖动纹理明显，显示效果不理想。</p>\n<h2 id=\"优化目标\">优化目标<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#优化目标\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>提升缩略图预览的视觉质量：减少锯齿、保留细线条/文字、过渡平滑</li>\n<li>不增加过多内存开销（MCU 堆内存有限，原缓冲区 ~18KB）</li>\n<li>不改变对外 API（<code>thermal_happy_set_ws_image_fit</code> 接口不变）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"技术方案演进\">技术方案演进<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#技术方案演进\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"第1版1bpp1bpp原有方案效果差\">第1版：1bpp→1bpp（原有方案，效果差）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#第1版1bpp1bpp原有方案效果差\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>源 1bpp (384×N) → 均匀区域采样 → 灰度 0~255\n→ 固定阈值 104 二值化 → Floyd-Steinberg 误差扩散\n→ 输出 1bpp LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_1BIT\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>问题</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>256 级灰度直接量化为 2 级（黑/白），误差扩散无法弥补</li>\n<li>均匀区域采样无边缘保护，文字和线条边缘模糊</li>\n<li>抖动纹理在 245×245 分辨率下肉眼可见</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"第2版1bpp4bpp过渡方案内存溢出\">第2版：1bpp→4bpp（过渡方案，内存溢出）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#第2版1bpp4bpp过渡方案内存溢出\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>源 1bpp → 中心加权区域采样 → 灰度 0~255\n→ 1.2× 对比度增益 + 稀疏墨点增强\n→ Floyd-Steinberg → 量化到 16 级灰度（4bpp）\n→ 输出 LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT（16色灰度调色板）\n→ LVGL 直接渲染\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>改进</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>16 级灰度（白→浅灰8级→深灰8级→黑），量化误差降至原来的 1/8</li>\n<li>中心加权采样（块中心 ±1/4 半径权重 ×2）</li>\n<li>蛇形扫描（serpentine）改善误差分布</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>问题</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>缓冲区需要 ~31KB（<code>LV_IMG_BUF_SIZE_INDEXED_4BIT(248,248)</code> = 31064 bytes）</li>\n<li>BK7252N 可用堆内存不足，<code>rt_malloc</code> 返回 NULL</li>\n<li>日志显示：<code>[ui] ws image parse failed, len=18576</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"第3版1bpp2bpp最终方案质量与内存平衡\">第3版：1bpp→2bpp（最终方案，质量与内存平衡）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#第3版1bpp2bpp最终方案质量与内存平衡\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>源 1bpp → 中心加权区域采样 → 灰度 0~255\n→ 1.2× 对比度增益 + 稀疏墨点增强\n→ Floyd-Steinberg → 量化到 4 级灰度（2bpp）\n→ 输出 LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_2BIT（4色灰度调色板）\n→ LVGL 直接渲染\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>优势</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>4 级灰度（白 → 浅灰 → 深灰 → 黑），比纯黑白提升明显</li>\n<li>缓冲区仅需 ~15.6KB（<code>LV_IMG_BUF_SIZE_INDEXED_2BIT(248,248)</code> = 15640 bytes）</li>\n<li>比原始 1bpp 方案的 ~18KB 还小，不会出现内存分配失败</li>\n<li>Floyd-Steinberg 误差扩散保留，过渡自然</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"涉及文件\">涉及文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#涉及文件\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/images/thermal_happy_lv.c</code></td><td><strong>核心修改</strong>：缩放渲染算法 + LVGL 图像格式</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/thermal_happy_lv.h</code></td><td>头文件（接口不变，无需修改）</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></td><td>调用方（无需修改，<code>lv_img_set_src</code> 透明处理格式变更）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"核心算法细节\">核心算法细节<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#核心算法细节\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-中心加权区域采样\">1. 中心加权区域采样<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-中心加权区域采样\"></a></h3>\n<p>当目标像素对应的源区域超过 1×1 像素时，采用中心加权计数：</p>\n<pre><code>源像素块中心 (cx, cy)，半径 (bw, bh)\n- 距离中心 ≤ 1/4 半径：权重 ×2（边缘保护）\n- 距离中心 > 1/4 半径：权重 ×1\n- 最终：gray = (black_weighted * 255) / (total_weighted)\n</code></pre>\n<p>比均匀 box filter 更好地保留文字/线条边缘。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-稀疏墨点增强\">2. 稀疏墨点增强<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-稀疏墨点增强\"></a></h3>\n<p>对于含墨量极低的源块（如细笔画中文字符），额外提升灰度避免被量化吞没：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>black <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">16</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> total<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  gray <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> GRAY_STEP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// &#x3C; 6.25% 墨点</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>black <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span>  <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> total<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  gray <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> GRAY_STEP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// &#x3C; 12.5% 墨点</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"3-2bpp-量化\">3. 2bpp 量化<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-2bpp-量化\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// GRAY_STEP = 85 (255/3)</span>\nlvl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>v <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">128</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">255</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 0..3</span>\nerror <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> v <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lvl <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">85</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// 误差用于扩散</span>\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>理想灰度</th><th>调色板 RGB</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>0</td><td>0 (白)</td><td>(255,255,255)</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>85 (浅灰)</td><td>(170,170,170)</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>170 (深灰)</td><td>(85,85,85)</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>255 (黑)</td><td>(0,0,0)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-自动反色检测\">4. 自动反色检测<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-自动反色检测\"></a></h3>\n<p>若输出图像 > 99.9% 像素为纯白（level 0），判定源数据反色，执行字节级 NOT 翻转。\n2bpp 格式下 <code>~byte</code> 天然正确翻转每个 2-bit 像素：<code>00?11, 01?10</code>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-蛇形扫描serpentine\">5. 蛇形扫描（Serpentine）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-蛇形扫描serpentine\"></a></h3>\n<p>偶数行从左到右扫描，奇数行从右到左，Floyd-Steinberg 误差扩散系数镜像对称，避免方向性伪影积累。</p>\n<h2 id=\"调色板反色问题修复\">调色板反色问题修复<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#调色板反色问题修复\"></a></h2>\n<p>初版 4bpp 实现中调色板方向与渲染逻辑不匹配：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>渲染逻辑：<code>gray=0</code>（无墨）→ 量化 level 0 → 应显示白色</li>\n<li>初版调色板：<code>pal[0] = RGB(0,0,0)</code> 黑色 ?</li>\n<li>修正后：<code>pal[0] = RGB(255,255,255)</code> 白色 ?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"参数配置\">参数配置<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#参数配置\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">THERMAL_PREVIEW_MAX_W</span>   <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">248U</span>   </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 缓冲区最大宽度（≥ 245 预览框）</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">THERMAL_PREVIEW_MAX_H</span>   <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">248U</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">THERMAL_GRAY_GAIN_Q8</span>    <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">307U</span>   </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 对比度增益 1.2× (Q8 定点)</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">THERMAL_SPARSE_BOOST_LO</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">3U</span>     </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 稀疏墨点增强 (&#x3C; 6.25%)</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">THERMAL_SPARSE_BOOST_HI</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">2U</span>     </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 稀疏墨点增强 (&#x3C; 12.5%)</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">GRAY_LEVELS</span>             <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">4U</span>     </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 2bpp: 4 级灰度</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">GRAY_STEP</span>               <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">85U</span>    </span><span class=\"token comment\">// 255 / (4-1)</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"内存对比\">内存对比<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#内存对比\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>方案</th><th>灰度级别</th><th>缓冲区大小</th><th>分配结果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>原始 1bpp</td><td>2</td><td>~18 KB</td><td>OK</td></tr><tr><td>4bpp（第2版）</td><td>16</td><td>~31 KB</td><td><strong>失败</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>2bpp（最终版）</strong></td><td><strong>4</strong></td><td><strong>~15.6 KB</strong></td><td><strong>OK</strong> ?</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"日志诊断\">日志诊断<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#日志诊断\"></a></h2>\n<p>新增内存分配失败诊断日志：</p>\n<pre><code>[thermal] alloc preview buf failed, size=31064\n</code></pre>\n<p>便于后续区分\"解析失败\"是内存不足还是数据格式问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"待优化方向\">待优化方向<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#待优化方向\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>若后续硬件升级或堆管理优化后有更多可用内存，可重新启用 4bpp 获得更细腻的灰度表现</li>\n<li>可考虑根据源图尺寸动态分配缓冲区（节省小图时的内存）</li>\n<li>稀疏墨点增强的参数可进一步调优，针对中文字符笔画特征优化</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/bk7252n-ai-printer\">BK7252N AI 打印机</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目开发记录总纲</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"个人开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"185a3f748171123c20ed21d8566347c8","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":51},"end":{"line":8,"column":9,"offset":57},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":69},"end":{"line":9,"column":23,"offset":89},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":3,"offset":138},"end":{"line":13,"column":15,"offset":150},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tutorial"}}],"anchors":{"个人开发笔记":{"type":"header","text":"个人开发笔记","value":"个人开发笔记","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"项目":{"type":"header","text":"项目","value":"项目","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"工作区":{"type":"header","text":"工作区","value":"工作区","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["c1bs7wsjfbhb0zipaywqv1","projects"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n# 个人开发笔记\n\n按**项目**组织的固件与软件开发文档（Dendron）。\n\n## 项目\n\n- [[项目]] — 全部项目索引\n- [[项目.BK7252N-AI打印机]] — BK7252N AI 打印机固件（RT-Thread + LVGL）\n\n## 工作区\n\n- [[tutorial]] — Dendron 使用教程\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none